ActionScript2 Compiling Kit
=====================================
This is a basic AS2 compiler package. 
Compiler included is for OSX, but the compiler website has binaries for Windows and Linux platforms as well.

Package includes:
* MTASC 1.12 for OSX
  http://www.mtasc.org/
* Macromedia Flash MX 2004 libraries

Examples (OSX)
=====================================
> export PATH=/CompileAS2/bin:/CompileAS2/mx2004/First Run/Classes:$PATH
> ./mtasc -cp "." -swf yourApplication.swf -mx com/example/Main.as -v